\b Communication\
\

\b0 Communication will be done via two ways: \
  (1)  issue a ticket in Git (look on the right side bar for \'93Issues\'94) or \
  (2) write an e-mail (either to everybody or just to the teaching assistant).\
\
The first one is preferred given that it\'92s easy to assign people that can work on the bug/enhancement/question and you can also close the issue when the problem has been fixed. \

