Why not a wiki?\
\

\b0 Several wikis were tested; none of them were suitable for our project. \
\

\i wikia.com 
\i0 - free hosting but no support for LaTeX; everybody can see it and change it;\

\i wiki.tudelft.nl 
\i0 - free hosting but incredibly slow; not active at all; no support for LaTeX; search engine is horrible; supports having users with different permissions though;\

\i gitwiki 
\i0 - there is a wiki embedded in the git repository; however it is very very simple and although only people with commit permissions can write on it it has no support for LaTeX formulas 	and other advanced document formatting tools.\
\
A Wikimedia website would be preferred, but we have no host for that at the moment.\
